// This formula displays a clickable Yahoo! Messenger icon indicating if the person is 
// logged on to the service. Users can click the icon to launch a Yahoo! Messenger 
// conversation with the person. This example uses a custom text field called Yahoo Name on 
// contacts where you can store the contact's Yahoo! Messenger ID.

HYPERLINK("ymsgr:sendIM?" & Yahoo_Name__c,
IMAGE("http://opi.yahoo.com/online?u=" & Yahoo_Name__c &
"&m;=g&t;=0", "Yahoo"))

